      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/biden-budget-calls-for-more-modest-growth-stubborn-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫预计 2024 年美国经济将显着降温，通胀将顽固（尽管温和）高于美联储的目标。]]></description>
