    <item>
      <title>拜登7.3万亿美元预算与特朗普展开税收斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/biden-s-7-3-trillion-budget-sets-spending-tax-fight-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的 7.3 万亿美元 2025 财年预算提案提出了第二任期愿景，即通过对富人和企业征收更高的税收来为选民提供更多服务、中产阶级税收减免和价格控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/biden-s-7-3-trillion-budget-sets-spending-tax-fight-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
